      "content": "---\ntitle: BC省雇主担保移民中对雇主的要求\nupdated: 2018-02-02 04:11:54Z\ncreated: 2018-02-02 04:11:37Z\nauthor: tangyongfeng@gmail.com\n---\n\n\n<en-note><div><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">雇主担保移民是</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">BC</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">省提名中的重要一项。</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">BC</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">省对雇主的要求如下：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">l&nbsp;</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">在</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">BC</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">省经营并有良好雇用记录；</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 1