nsform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">如果是大温地区，雇主单位至少应有</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">5</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">名及以上全职员工；大温之外，雇主单位至少应有</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">3</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">名及以上全职员工；</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">l&nbsp;</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">具有良好的工作和商业记录；</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">l&nbsp;</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">签署雇主宣言；</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">l&nbsp;</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-indent: -21pt; -en-paragraph: true;\">满足加拿大国内劳务市场的雇工条件；</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">对于</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">NOC O/A/B</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">类职业，招聘广告必须公开</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">14</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">天以上，政府承认的招聘渠道有：热门招聘网站、专业招聘网站、全国性报纸、专业期刊等。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">招聘广告中必须包括以下内容：</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">公司名称、岗位名称和从事内容、工资、工作地点、联系方式、岗位申请要求（教育</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">/</span><span STYLE=\"border: 0px; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; -en-paragraph: true;\">证书、工作经验）。</span></div><div STYLE=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-wrap: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 21px; color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-caps: